&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Opportunity&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for a forward-thinking, hands-on Manager of Sales Operations to modernize the engine room of our sales organization. While this role oversees the Sales Operations function, your primary mission will be to evolve our &quot;lead-to-quote&quot; journey from a manual workflow into an AI-augmented, frictionless, and highly scalable ecosystem.&lt;/p&gt;
