&lt;li&gt;Partner with customers on structured change management strategies to ensure sustained adoption and value realization.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Data-Driven Value Realization &amp;amp; Commercial Impact&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
